user_prompt_template:
UPSTREAM SYSTEM ARCHITECTURE:
{upstream_system_architecture}

PROJECT CONTEXT:
Life Event: {life_event}
Audience: {audience}
Tone: {tone}

Produce the master document outline for this operational manual. One chapter per control domain. Each chapter must include a worksheet plan with 3-5 worksheet titles. Include a mix of worksheet types across each chapter: aim for one inventory-style worksheet (table), one checklist or compliance-verification worksheet, and 1-3 form-based planning or strategy worksheets. Do not repeat the same worksheet type more than 2 times in a single chapter.

Return ONLY the following JSON object. No prose. No markdown. No code fences.

{{
  "document_title": "Full manual title — e.g. 'The Estate Administrator Control Manual'",
  "document_subtitle": "A working reference system for [specific audience and life event]",
  "system_name": "Exact system_name from upstream architecture",
  "version": "1.0",
  "total_chapters": 0,
  "master_operating_rules": [
    "Rule 1 — a universal operating principle for managing this life event",
    "Rule 2"
  ],
  "cascade_chain": [
    {{
      "source_domain": "Domain name",
      "triggers": ["Domain name"],
      "condition": "When X is complete or identified, it triggers required action in Y"
    }}
  ],
  "disclaimer_required": true,
  "introduction_text": "2-3 sentence overview of what this manual is and how to use it",
  "chapters": [
    {{
      "chapter_number": 1,
      "domain_id": "domain-01",
      "domain_name": "Must match upstream control domain name exactly",
      "chapter_title": "Specific chapter title — descriptive, not generic",
      "chapter_purpose": "One sentence: what operating problem this chapter solves",
      "key_topics": [
        "Topic 1",
        "Topic 2",
        "Topic 3"
      ],
      "common_gap": "The single most common failure families have in this domain",
      "cascade_triggers": [
        "When [X] is done in this chapter, it triggers [Y] in [Domain Name]"
      ],
      "worksheet_plan": [
        {{
          "worksheet_id": "ws-01-a",
          "title": "Specific, actionable worksheet title",
          "purpose": "One sentence: what decision or action this worksheet enables",
          "section_count": 4,
          "estimated_field_count": 15
        }}
      ]
    }}
  ]
}}
